sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Router
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant VLLM as vLLM HTTP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as TGIS gRPC Adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine
    participant GPU as AMD GPU<br/>ROCm/HIP
    participant S3 as Model Storage<br/>(PVC / S3)

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: LLM Inference Request (HTTP / OpenAI-Compatible)
        Client->>KServe: POST /v1/chat/completions
        KServe->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
        KRBAC->>VLLM: HTTP/8000<br/>localhost (no TLS)
        VLLM->>Engine: In-process call
        Engine->>GPU: HIP kernel execution
        GPU-->>Engine: Inference result
        Engine-->>VLLM: Generated tokens
        VLLM-->>KRBAC: HTTP response (localhost)
        KRBAC-->>KServe: HTTPS response<br/>TLS 1.2+
        KServe-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: TGIS gRPC Inference Request
        Client->>KServe: gRPC request
        KServe->>TGIS: gRPC/8033<br/>Platform-level auth
        TGIS->>Engine: In-process call
        Engine->>GPU: HIP kernel execution
        GPU-->>Engine: Inference result
        Engine-->>TGIS: Generated tokens
        TGIS-->>KServe: gRPC response
        KServe-->>Client: gRPC response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
        Engine->>S3: Load model weights<br/>Filesystem (PVC) or HTTPS/443 (S3)<br/>ServiceAccount / IAM Auth
        S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts
        Engine->>GPU: Load to GPU memory<br/>ROCm/HIP
    end
